resources.string: Shows indicator notification for a meeting
Camera access is required to display the camera preview.
Camera could not be opened.\nThis occurs when the camera is not available (for example it is already in use) or if the system has denied access (for example when camera access has been disabled).
Camera permission was granted. Starting preview.

Audio record could not be opened.\nThis occurs when the audio record is not available (for example it is already in use) or if the system has denied access (for example when audio record access has been disabled).
Audio record access is required to display the audio record preview.
Permission is not available. Requesting audio record permission.
Audio record permission request was denied.
